des:
You can use fullorange smart skill to control smart lights, smart plug etc smart device in your house by voice.
fullorange smart app could control and scene your smart devices at home

After connecting Alexa to your Fullorange Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Fullorange Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one App name account in our "Fullorange Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Fullorange Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Fullorange Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Fullorange Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Fullorange Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Fullorange Smart", and you'll be navigated to Fullorange Smart login page;
(9). Input your Fullorange Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

* Alexa , turn on kitchen light
* Alexa, turn off kitchen light
* Alexa, dim livingroom light
* Alexa, brighten livingroom light
* Alexa set the livingroom light to 20 percent
* Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
